text: Franziska Becskehazy (born 7 February 1966) is a Brazilian cross-country skier. She competed in the women's 10 kilometre classical at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Brazil Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rio de Janeiro (city)
